    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-maintained ride? This car is in great shape and ready for its next adventure! It has been well cared for, offering a smooth driving experience and a clean interior that shows it's been a dependable companion. It's a fantastic choice for anyone who wants quality and performance without the brand-new price tag!",
