    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention from its next owner. While the body is mostly intact, the engine has a persistent oil leak and the transmission is shifting very roughly, indicating it may need a rebuild soon. The interior shows heavy wear and tear, and several electronic components are currently non-functional. It is being sold as-is, making it an ideal project car for someone with the tools and expertise to restore it to its former glory.",
