    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a budget-friendly starter? This car has seen plenty of road and is ready for someone with a little DIY spirit to give it some TLC! While it shows significant wear and will need some mechanical attention to get back to its best, it's a great opportunity to own a vehicle at a fraction of the usual cost.",
